race.comment: STREAMLINED (13) is another debutant the Grantham barn produce today who looks to have plenty of ability. His latest trial with the Blinkers on was very impressive and they remain on for his raceday debut. Looks an exciting prospect on debut. GRAVITY DEFYING (12) draws the inside pole off a nice trial at Belmont most recently and the booking of Brad Parnham suggests he's ready to fire on debut. YALDA NIGHT (4) is knocking on the door of a maiden win, finishing 1.8L off the winner at Northam last start. That was over the mile, though his run two back at Toodyay was similar at this trip. Well drawn and can feature in the finish. MASMELO (16) strikes a suitable race third-up into the campaign and with a touch of luck from the barrier, she can make her presence felt.
